msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:45 of
msgid ""
"Overall view of discrete Fourier transforms, with definitions and "
"conventions used."
msgstr "离散傅里叶变换的总体视图，包括所使用的定义和约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:47 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:48 of
msgid "The forward *n*-dimensional FFT, of which `ifftn` is the inverse."
msgstr "前向 *n* 维 FFT，`ifftn` 是其逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:50 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:51 of
msgid "The one-dimensional inverse FFT."
msgstr "一维逆 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:53 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:54 of
msgid "The two-dimensional inverse FFT."
msgstr "二维逆 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:56 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifftshift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:57 of
msgid "Undoes `fftshift`, shifts zero-frequency terms to beginning of tensor."
msgstr "取消 `fftshift`，将零频率项移至张量的开头。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:60 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:61 of
msgid "See `mt.fft` for definitions and conventions used."
msgstr "有关所使用的定义和约定，请参见 `mt.fft`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ifftn.ifftn:63 of
msgid ""
"Zero-padding, analogously with `ifft`, is performed by appending zeros to"
" the input along the specified dimension.  Although this is the common "
"approach, it might lead to surprising results.  If another form of zero "
"padding is desired, it must be performed before `ifftn` is called."
msgstr ""
"与 `ifft` 类似，零填充是通过在指定维度上向输入追加零来实现的。尽管这是"
"常见做法，但可能会导致令人意外的结果。如果需要其他形式的零填充，必须在"
"调用 `ifftn` 之前完成。"

